AVM — Adaptive Volume Mode
Copyright 2026 Tom Demitras

Constant-tool-load per-level optimization for Fusion 360 adaptive
clearing. Developed by Tom Demitras — machining physics validation,
empirical CAM behavior discovery (minimumAxialEngagement level
selection, FAD interaction), and instrumented cut verification — in
collaboration with Claude (Anthropic) — physics modeling, solver, and
Fusion API implementation.

First validated cut: 2026-07-08, Delrin, Haas Mini Mill.
